{
  "stem": "3659.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I have investments here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I have businesses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I have apartment houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We can't just leave like this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, let's go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says, no, we're not leaving.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And within two days, my father's business, three men walked in in brown shirts and says, from this moment on, we're running your businesses.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We will let you stay here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when it comes to what we take in in monies, we will let you know how much you can keep and what we are taking.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was the very first sign.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The second one was, within three or four days big signs in grocery stores, [GERMAN], means we don't serve dogs and Jews, and the same was on park benches.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And after two days, we went out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the one thing that I would like to make-- that really was one of the major factors that made us survive-- we were blond and blue-eyed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother, my sister, myself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father was-- had brown hair.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that really was one of the very major factors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as-- after-- as I said, after the two days and three days passed, and the pomp and circumstance that they carried on with marching bands, the pictures that you may have seen on newsreels with thousands of people marching, these were the facts.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I saw it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went on the streets.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I was not that afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Being a 13, 14-year-old child, you don't have the intense fear that an adult will fear.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so it was very unusual for me, you know, especially where you led a life like we did, so sheltered.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And here was all this going on, and the bands were playing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was mass hypnosis that they exerted against or to the people.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
